deck: When Tails is injured in a battle with Doctor Eggman, Sonic holds auditions for a new sidekick to replace him.
name: The Sidekick

deck: While his evil lair is undergoing repairs, Dr. Eggman crashes on Tails' couch and proves to be a very difficult roommate.
name: Can an Evil Genius Crash on Your Couch for a Few Weeks?

description: When a Gothamite is found beaten to death, Gordon and Bullock are intrigued by the motive and take on the case. Meanwhile, Bruce returns to school and has trouble making friends.
name: The Mask

description: Trying to close the Wayne murder case, a young Harvey Dent (guest star Nicholas D'Agosto) and Gordon team up, much to Mayor James' (guest star Richard Kind) chagrin. Meanwhile, Penguin makes contact with Mooney's (Jada Pinkett Smith) secret weapon, Liza (guest star Mackenzie Leigh).
name: Harvey Dent

description: While on a supply run, Hera and Sabine find themselves stranded but not alone in a seemingly abandoned locale.
name: Out of Darkness

description: A refugee of the Empire seeks the Rebels' help to get off the planet with important information.
name: Empire Day

deck: After being invited to a fancy gala, Sticks admits she does not know how to behave in a lady-like manner.
name: Translate This

deck: In hopes of having new additions to his traveling circus, a ringmaster captures Sonic and his friends.
name: Buster

description: Captain Irving's daughter is targeted by evil forces, so he pleads for help from Crane and Mills, and also looks to Washington's Bible for answers. Meanwhile, another frightening chapter of Jenny's past is revealed.
name: The Vessel

description: After a body is found strung up in the Wildcat gym, Ted Grant becomes the main suspect. Oliver and Laurel argue over Teds innocence. Meanwhile, in flashbacks, when Maseo needs Oliver to remember where an informant for China White stashed key information, he asks Tatsu to help jog Olivers memory. Roy shares a secret with Felicity.
name: Guilty

deck: Skye's having bad dreams, and feel a sense of impending doom. Coulson wants to destroy the alien city before HYDRA gets there with the obelisk.
description:
Skye tells Raina that Hydra has the obelisk. Raina tries to get captured by HYDRA, but is S.H.I.E.L.D. prevents it. On the flight to San Juan, Raina tells Skye that her father who is working with HYDRA found her in Thailand and mentored her, and that he never stopped looking for Skye. She also claims that the Obelisk is a "Diviner", a Kree artifact that determines who is worthy of inheriting the Earth.

HYDRA quinjets surround the Bus and a party of HYDRA agents, led by Ward, board the ship and take Raina and Skye, as well as the data on the location of the city.
name: Ye Who Enter Here

has_staff_review.name: Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. Episode 208 - "...Ye Who Enter Here"

description: AUSTIN BUTLER (THE CARRIE DIARIES) JOINS THE CAST AS CHASE; OLIVER DEALS WITH CARRIE CUTTER Oliver (Stephen Amell) must stop an Arrow-obsessed serial killer, Carrie Cutter (guest star Amy Gumenick), who is convinced that The Arrow is her one true love and will stop at nothing to get his attention. Unfortunately, her way of getting his attention is to kill people. Meanwhile, Ray (Brandon Routh) asks Felicity (Emily Bett Rickards) to be his date for a work dinner with important clients. Thea (Willa Holland) auditions new DJs for Verdant and meets Chase (Austin Butler), a brash DJ with whom she immediately clashes.
name: Draw Back Your Bow

description: GREG FINLEY GUEST STARS AS DC COMICS VILLAIN GIRDER The Flash (Grant Gustin) faces a new meta-human named Tony (guest star Greg Finley, Star-Crossed, Secret Life of the American Teenager), who can turn himself into girded steel at will. While Dr. Wells (Tom Cavanagh) and Caitlin (Danielle Panabaker) are concerned about Barrys safety, Cisco (Carlos Valdes) comes up with a plan to take Tony down. Meanwhile, Iriss (Candice Patton) blog on The Flash gets her into trouble, and Eddie (Rick Cosnett) witnesses Tonys abilities firsthand and begins to ask questions that Joe (Jesse L. Martin) doesnt want answered. Joe asks Dr. Wells to help him solve Nora Allens murder.
name: The Flash is Born

has_staff_review.name: The Flash Episode 106 - "The Flash is Born"

deck: The Ninja Turtles are trapped in their own dreams and being attacked by frightening beavers. It's up to April and Casey to save them!
name: In Dreams

description: JONJO O'NEILL GUEST STARS -- When Constantine's (Matt Ryan) old friend Gary Lester (guest star Jonjo O'Neill) accidentally releases a powerful demon in Atlanta, John is forced to determine exactly what he is prepared to sacrifice in his battle with the underworld. Harold Perrineau and Anglica Celaya also star.
name: A Feast of Friends

description:
In New Orleans, Constantines (Matt Ryan) unusual knowledge of a string of crimes gets him into trouble with Detective Jim Corrigan (guest star Emmett Scanlan). He must form an unholy alliance with Papa Midnite (guest star Michael James Shaw) when a voodoo ritual to help people communicate with their dead loved ones takes a deadly turn.

Charles Halford and Anglica Celaya also star.
name: Danse Vaudou

description: Cautiously, members of our group must venture into a familiar location on a heroic rescue mission. It's a huge stage, but so are the stakes.
name: Consumed
